Svisskipting

hverfi <- c(400, 320, 600)
hj <- filter(hj, matssvaedi%in%hverfi)

Vi kvum a nota 400, 540, og 600. Vi breyttum svo ger eirra flokkabreytu me vieigandi nfnum.

Fermetraver

hj <- hj %>%
      mutate(fermetraverd = kaupverd/birtm2)

Tegund Fasteigna

hj <- hj %>% mutate(teg_eign_s_i = 
                      fct_recode(teg_eign, 
                                 Srbli = 'Einblishs', 
                                 Srbli = 'Parhs', 
                                 Srbli = 'Rahs', 
                                 b = 'bareign'))

Hluti 2 - Myndrn Framsetning

Kaupver og Fermetragildi

graph1 <- hj %>%
  ggplot(aes(x=kaupverd)) + geom_histogram(color='purple', bins=50) + 
  xlab('Kaupver') + ylab('Fjldi')

graph2 <- hj %>%
  ggplot(aes(x=birtm2)) + geom_histogram(color='purple', bins=50) + 
  xlab('Fermetrar') + ylab('Fjldi')

plot_row <- plot_grid(graph1, graph2)
title <- plot_grid(ggdraw() + draw_label('Kaupver', fontface = 'bold'), 
                   ggdraw() + draw_label('Fermetrar', fontface = 'bold'))

plot_grid(title, plot_row, ncol=1, rel_heights = c(0.1, 1))

Fjldi eigna eftir hverfum og tegundum

hj %>% 
  group_by(matssvaedi, teg_eign_s_i) %>% 
  summarize(n = n(), na.rm=TRUE) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x=matssvaedi, y = n, fill=teg_eign_s_i)) + 
  xlab('Hverfi') + ylab('Heildarfjldi Eigna') + labs(fill='Eignartegund') + geom_bar(stat="identity", position='dodge')

Fermetraver eigna eftir tegundum eigna

hj %>% ggplot(aes(x = teg_eign_s_i, y = fermetraverd)) + 
        geom_boxplot() + xlab('Ger eigna') + ylab('Fermetraver (s.kr)')

Str eigna & kaupver skipt upp eftir hverfum

hj %>% group_by(matssvaedi) %>%
  summarize(kaupverd, birtm2, teg_eign_s_i, na.RM=TRUE) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = kaupverd, y = birtm2, color=teg_eign_s_i)) + geom_point() + 
  facet_grid(rows = vars(matssvaedi)) + xlab('Kaupver (s. kr)') + ylab('Str (m^2)') + labs(color='Tegund Eigna') + 
  xlim(5000, 100000)

Fasteignaver

hj %>% group_by(matssvaedi, teg_eign_s_i) %>%
  summarise(
    n = n(),
    medal = mean(fermetraverd, na.rm=TRUE),
    midg = median(fermetraverd, na.rm=TRUE),
    stadl = sd(fermetraverd, na.rm=TRUE)
  ) %>% 
  kable(align="c", col.names = c('Matssvi','Tegund', 
        'Fjldi', 'Mealtal', 'Migildi', 'Staalfrvik')) %>% 
  kable_styling('striped') %>%
  add_header_above(c(' '=3, 'Fermetraver'=3))

Texti m/ treikningum.

Gerum n r fyrir a vi sum a vinna me hverfi strreykjavkursvinu ar sem 20% eigna eru einblishs. Hugsum okkur n a vi veljum 3 eignir hverfinu af handahfi.

  • Lkurnar v a tvr eignir su einblishs eru 0.384.
  • Lkurnar v a frri en tvr eignir su einblishs eru 0.104.

Gerum n r fyrir a str einblishsa hverfinu fylgi normaldreifingu me mealtal 170 fm og staalfrvik 20 fm.

  • Lkurnar v a eign, sem er valin a handahfi, s strri en 190 \(fm^2\) eru 0.1586553.
  • Til ess a Jonni s hp eirra 10% me strstu eignirnar, arf hsi hans a vera 195.6310313 \(fm^2\).
